**Godot:** `15-godot-mobile-landscape-ux.mdc` · [docs/README_02](docs/README_02_GAMEPLAY_VISUAL_UX_REPLAYABILITY.md) §16.

Mobile landscape UX rules:

- Design for thumbs and safe areas.
- Core HUD: lives/gold/Sacred Fire/wave; pause/speed; hero; tower cards; contextual actions.
- Large touch targets; icons over long labels during waves.
- Fast tower placement: tap spot → choose tower.
- Do not block gameplay with oversized panels during waves unless paused.
